goals.title: Build a Healthier Morning Routine
goals.description: Start each day with a short activity that promotes focus and self-awareness. The goal is to increase structure and positivity in the first 30 minutes of my day.

goals.title: Rediscover Joy Through Hobbies
goals.description: Set aside time weekly to engage in hobbies that bring you joy. The goal is to reconnect with personal interests and foster a sense of play and creativity.
